{"words":[{"word":"playername","count":2},{"word":"deviation","count":2},{"word":"calculations","count":2},{"word":"account","count":2},{"word":"model","count":2},{"word":"peaks","count":2},{"word":"prestige","count":2},{"word":"human","count":2},{"word":"theory","count":2},{"word":"lost","count":1},{"word":"input","count":1},{"word":"parameters","count":1},{"word":"perfect","count":1},{"word":"results","count":1},{"word":"deviate","count":1},{"word":"unless","count":1},{"word":"mornye","count":1},{"word":"talking","count":1},{"word":"tiny","count":1},{"word":"given","count":1},{"word":"enough","count":1},{"word":"completely","count":1},{"word":"overwrite","count":1},{"word":"expected","count":1},{"word":"future","count":1},{"word":"state","count":1},{"word":"variable","count":1},{"word":"proposed","count":1},{"word":"system","count":1},{"word":"simple","count":1},{"word":"holds","count":1},{"word":"true","count":1},{"word":"though","count":1},{"word":"figure","count":1},{"word":"introduced","count":1},{"word":"detect","count":1},{"word":"follow","count":1},{"word":"logic","count":1},{"word":"implying","count":1},{"word":"emotion","count":1},{"word":"interfere","count":1},{"word":"create","count":1},{"word":"unpredictable","count":1},{"word":"outcomes","count":1},{"word":"somewhat","count":1},{"word":"inspiring","count":1},{"word":"fundamentally","count":1},{"word":"sound","count":1},{"word":"so-called","count":1},{"word":"factor","count":1},{"word":"cannot","count":1},{"word":"quantified","count":1},{"word":"infinite","count":1},{"word":"branching","count":1},{"word":"paths","count":1},{"word":"snowflake's","count":1},{"word":"unique","count":1},{"word":"formation","count":1},{"word":"ah","count":1},{"word":"never","count":1},{"word":"mind","count":1},{"word":"i'll","count":1},{"word":"chew","count":1},{"word":"later","count":1},{"word":"course","count":1},{"word":"ultra-hardcore","count":1},{"word":"duelist","count":1},{"word":"interesting","count":1},{"word":"game","count":1},{"word":"years","count":1},{"word":"oh","count":1},{"word":"watch","count":1},{"word":"opponents'","count":1},{"word":"carefully","count":1},{"word":"designed","count":1},{"word":"strategies","count":1},{"word":"decks","count":1},{"word":"walk","count":1},{"word":"into","count":1},{"word":"bugs","count":1},{"word":"caught","count":1},{"word":"spider's","count":1},{"word":"web","count":1},{"word":"helplessly","count":1},{"word":"awaiting","count":1},{"word":"doom","count":1},{"word":"victory","count":1},{"word":"mathematics","count":1},{"word":"exhilarating","count":1},{"word":"zero","count":1},{"word":"interest","count":1},{"word":"disbanding","count":1},{"word":"any","count":1},{"word":"club","count":1},{"word":"professor","count":1},{"word":"calith","count":1},{"word":"promised","count":1},{"word":"worked","count":1},{"word":"i'd","count":1},{"word":"shortage","count":1},{"word":"powerful","count":1},{"word":"duelists","count":1},{"word":"wanting","count":1},{"word":"challenge","count":1},{"word":"honest","count":1},{"word":"wrong","count":1},{"word":"challengers","count":1},{"word":"duel","count":1},{"word":"brilliantly","count":1},{"word":"satisfying","count":1},{"word":"feeling","count":1},{"word":"giving","count":1},{"word":"short","count":1},{"word":"hurts","count":1},{"word":"worst","count":1},{"word":"huh","count":1},{"word":"perhaps","count":1},{"word":"mathematical","count":1},{"word":"models","count":1},{"word":"modifications","count":1},{"word":"next","count":1},{"word":"time","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"I... lost?! But all the input parameters were perfect... How could the results deviate this much...?","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"...Unless... {PlayerName}, you're the one... Could this be what Mornye was talking about?","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"...A tiny deviation, given enough calculations, can completely overwrite the expected future state.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Just like that variable I couldn't account for in my proposed model.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Even in a system as simple as Peaks of Prestige, it holds true. Though I can't figure out how you introduced a deviation that even I couldn't detect...","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"That's it? No... If I follow that logic... Are you implying that human will and emotion can interfere with theory to create unpredictable outcomes?","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"...Very well, this is somewhat inspiring. But fundamentally, even if this theory is sound, this so-called \"human factor\" cannot even be quantified...","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"The model would need to account for infinite branching paths, like a snowflake's unique formation... Ah, never mind. I'll chew on it later.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Of course not. I'm an ultra-hardcore duelist! I think Peaks of Prestige is the most interesting game to come out in years!","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Oh, to watch my opponents' carefully designed strategies and decks walk right into my calculations, like bugs caught in a spider's web, helplessly awaiting their doom...","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"It's a victory for mathematics! It's exhilarating!","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"I have zero interest in disbanding any club. But Professor Calith promised that if I worked with him, I'd have no shortage of powerful duelists wanting to challenge me...","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"To be honest, he wasn't wrong. But out of all the challengers, only our duel was brilliantly satisfying.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"This feeling of giving it your all, only to come up just short... it hurts, but it's not the worst, huh?","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Perhaps. Well then, my mathematical models need some modifications. Until next time, {PlayerName}.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019}]}